# R3F Scene Rules

- Scene components are **slaves to Zustand state**. No physics calculations in render.
- Use low-poly primitives (`<mesh>`, `<boxGeometry>`) until real models are added.
- Parent-child scene graph: `RobotCar > Chassis > Axle > Wheel`.
- Use `useFrame` for animation, subscribe to stores with `useStore` selectors.
- All 3D components must be `"use client"` and loaded with `dynamic({ ssr: false })`.
